SUMMARY:Last 2 Saturdays of March - A/B/C long ride - EP New Witness Tree 
 Ride (32F)
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nThis is a Show & Go ride 
 with anticipated average pace of 15-18 mph.\n\nThese are the final winter 
 season long rides. Group will attempt to stay together\, but riders must b
 e willing and able to maintain at least a 15 mph avg. If that is not possi
 ble\, please consider joining the winter season short rides.\n\nCue and GP
 X: https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/ep-new-witness-tree-trek-33f/\
 n\nHelmets are mandatory. No earbuds. Please bring water and a basic repai
 r kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\n\nTo eliminate pass
 ing around a pen and paper waiver\, we require an LBC Club membership and 
 Meetup RSVP below to join this ride.\n\nBeing on Meetup does not mean you 
 are a club member. [Join here](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.a
 spx?page_id=60&club_id=257148).\n\nYour RSVP is your agreement to abide by
  the club's [Code of Conduct](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content
 .aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984)\,\n\n[Rules of the Road]
 (https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=2571
 48&module_id=325159)\, and [Ride Waiver](https://lancasterbikeclub.net/doc
 s.ashx?id=454318)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3138307
 54/
